contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.EmailPreviewText: Check out the latest news 📰 from the Kentico community!
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.EmailSubject: September's Refresh, new developer resources, and our first Expert Chat episode
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.NewsletterEmailIntroContent:
Hey {!ResolveDynamicText("Recipient.FirstName","friend")!} ,

Did you realize we've already reached email #10 in this newsletter series? Thanks for subscribing and we hope you'll be with us for newsletter #100 and #1,000 😅! 

Now, for this week's Kentico Community Newsletter we feature our first Expert Chat to discuss the overlap of marketing strategy and software developer knowledge, September's Refresh, new developer resources from our training team, and several community contributions. Enjoy!
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.NewsletterEmailOutroContent: If you found the information in this newsletter helpful, something looks strange in your email client, or you have news, a video, or blot post to feature in a future newsletter - let us know by giving us some feedback.
